  27:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       After reset the device is running from High Speed Internal oscillator
  28:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (64 MHz) with Flash 3 wait states. Flash prefetch buffer, D-Cache
  29:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       and I-Cache are disabled, and all peripherals are off except internal
