  30:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       SRAM, Flash and JTAG.
  31:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c **** 
  32:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) There is no prescaler on High speed (AHBs) and Low speed (APBs) busses:
  33:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****           all peripherals mapped on these busses are running at HSI speed.
  34:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) The clock for all peripherals is switched off, except the SRAM and FLASH.
  35:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) All GPIOs are in analog mode, except the JTAG pins which
  36:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****           are assigned to be used for debug purpose.
  37:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c **** 
