1287:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @brief  Select the clock source to output on MCO1 pin(PA8) or on MCO2 pin(PC9).
1288:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   PA8/PC9 should be configured in alternate function mode.
1289:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @param  RCC_MCOx  specifies the output direction for the clock source.
1290:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *          For STM32H5xx family this parameter can have only one value:
1291:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            @arg @ref RCC_MCO1  Clock source to output on MCO1 pin(PA8).
1292:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            @arg @ref RCC_MCO2  Clock source to output on MCO2 pin(PC9).
1293:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @param  RCC_MCOSource  specifies the clock source to output.
1294:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
1295:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            @arg RCC_MCO1SOURCE_HSI: HSI clock selected as MCO1 source
1296:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            @arg RCC_MCO1SOURCE_LSE: LSE clock selected as MCO1 source
1297:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            @arg RCC_MCO1SOURCE_HSE: HSE clock selected as MCO1 source
