1831:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @brief  Get the attribute of an RCC item.
1832:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   Secure and non-secure attributes are only available from secure state
1833:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         when the system implements the security (TZEN=1)
1834:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @param  Item Single item to get secure/non-secure and privilege/non-privilege attribute from.
